{"type":null,"faqId":20261,"title":"¿Qué puedo hacer si la conexión Wi-Fi de mi teléfono termina automáticamente después de que se apague la pantalla?","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.0in 1.0in 1.0in 1.0in;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.045138888in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.22222222in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.p6{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:1.6381944in;margin-top:0.027777778in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>Cambiar la política de suspensión de Wi-Fi de la siguiente manera: Toque </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=68449\" style=\"width:0.22083333in;height:0.20833333in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> </span><span class=\"s1\">Configuración</span><span>, vaya a </span><span class=\"s1\">Conexiones inalámbricas y redes</span><span>, y toca </span><span class=\"s1\">Wi-Fi</span><span>. Toque&gt;</span><span class=\"s1\"> Avanzado</span><span>&gt; </span><span class=\"s1\">Mantener Wi-Fi durante la suspensión</span><span>. A continuación, seleccione </span><span class=\"s1\">Siempre</span><span>. </span>\n</p>\n<p  >Figure 1-1<span>Establecimiento de la política de suspensión de Wi-Fi</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=68450\" style=\"width:1.7347223in;height:3.0770833in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=68451\" style=\"width:1.7444445in;height:3.1125in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=68452\" style=\"width:1.7694445in;height:3.148611in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=68453\" style=\"width:0.59305555in;height:0.1736111in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>Por defecto, se selecciona siempre para Mantener Wi-Fi durante la suspensión. Si se modifican los ajustes, su teléfono se desconecta de la red Wi-Fi cuando la pantalla se apaga. A continuación se describen las tres opciones de Mantener Wi-Fi durante la suspensión:</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span class=\"s1\">Siempre</span><span>: Mantener en nunca desconectar de una conexión Wi-Fi.</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span class=\"s1\">Sólo cuando está enchufado</span><span>: Nunca desconecte de una conexión Wi-Fi cuando el teléfono se está cargando. Si el teléfono no se carga, se desconecta de la conexión Wi-Fi cuando ha estado inactivo durante 3 minutos.</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><a name=\"_Toc342402049\"><span class=\"s1\">Nunca (aumenta el uso de datos)</span><span>: Desconecte de una conexión Wi-Fi cuando el teléfono no se usa durante 3 minutos</span><span>.</span></a>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":103,"languageName":"es","faqCode":"3801","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1426193024000,"seriesProductName":"C8860V,CM990,EDGE-U00,G510-0251,G526-L22,G526-L33,G620S-L01,G620S-L03,G630-U251,G6-L11,G6-L33,G760-L03,Jazz-L09,MT1-U06,P2-6011,Sophia-L12,U8815-51,U9200-1,U9202L-1,U9508,U9510E,Y220-U00,Y221-U03,Y221-U12,Y221-U33,Y300-0151,Y320-U10,Y320-U151,Y321-U051,Y360-U23,Y511-U251,Y520-U33,Y550-L01,Y550-L03,Y600-U151,Y625-U03","visitedTimes":28,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"conexión, wi-fi, termina, automáticamente, apague, pantalla, Android 4.4","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}